column16: Matt den Dekker grounds out, second baseman Nick Franklin to first baseman Rene Rivera.
Ian Desmond singles on a ground ball to first baseman Rene Rivera.   Danny Espinosa to 2nd.
Michael Taylor pops out to catcher Curt Casali in foul territory.
Danny Espinosa singles on a line drive to center fielder Kevin Kiermaier.
Clint Robinson flies out to left fielder David DeJesus.
Wilson Ramos homers (6) on a fly ball to center field.
